# 12. Traversing 2D Array

```java
int[][] arr = {
    {10,20,30},
    {40,50,60}
};

for(int i=0;i<arr.length;i++){
    for(int j=0;j<arr[i].length;j++){
        System.out.print(arr[i][j]+" ");
    }
    System.out.println();
}
```

### Output

```java
10 20 30
40 50 60
```

