# 15. Passing Array to Method

```java
class Test {

    static void display(int[] arr){

        for(int x : arr){
            System.out.println(x);
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int[] arr = {10,20,30};

        display(arr);
    }
}
```

