# 17. Array of Objects

```java
class Student {

    int id;

    Student(int id){
        this.id = id;
    }
}

public class Test {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Student[] students = new Student[3];

        students[0] = new Student(101);
        students[1] = new Student(102);
        students[2] = new Student(103);

        for(Student s : students){
            System.out.println(s.id);
        }
    }
}
```

