# 20. Searching in Array

## Linear Search

```java
int[] arr = {10,20,30,40};
int key = 30;

for(int i=0;i<arr.length;i++){

    if(arr[i] == key){
        System.out.println("Found");
        break;
    }
}
```

---

## Binary Search

```java
import java.util.Arrays;

int[] arr = {10,20,30,40,50};

int index = Arrays.binarySearch(arr,30);

System.out.println(index);
```

