# 24. Important Interview Programs

## Find Largest Element

```java
int[] arr = {10,50,30,20};

int max = arr[0];

for(int x : arr){

    if(x > max){
        max = x;
    }
}

System.out.println(max);
```

---

## Find Smallest Element

```java
int[] arr = {10,50,30,20};

int min = arr[0];

for(int x : arr){

    if(x < min){
        min = x;
    }
}

System.out.println(min);
```

---

## Sum of Array

```java
int[] arr = {10,20,30,40};

int sum = 0;

for(int x : arr){
    sum += x;
}

System.out.println(sum);
```

---

## Average of Array

```java
int[] arr = {10,20,30,40};

int sum = 0;

for(int x : arr){
    sum += x;
}

double avg = (double)sum/arr.length;

System.out.println(avg);
```

---

## Reverse Array

```java
int[] arr = {10,20,30,40};

for(int i=arr.length-1;i>=0;i--){
    System.out.print(arr[i]+" ");
}
```

