# 26. Advantages of Arrays

* Fast access using index
* Less memory overhead
* Easy traversal
* Stores multiple values together

---

# 27. Disadvantages of Arrays

* Fixed size
* Same data type only
* Insertion/Deletion difficult
* Memory wastage possible

